---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — vinReliability"
  description="Terms of service for vinReliability LLC products including vinQuality, vinFMEA, and vinReliability."
  keywords="vinReliability terms of service, vinQuality terms, SaaS terms"
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="reveal">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
            Terms of Service
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Terms Content -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="reveal prose prose-slate max-w-none">

          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the products and services provided by vinReliability LLC ("we," "us," or "our"), including vinQuality, vinFMEA, vinReliability, and the vinqms.com website. By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms.
          </p>

          <!-- Acceptance of Terms -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            By creating an account, purchasing a subscription, or using any of our products, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms. If you are using our services on behalf of an organization, you represent that you have the authority to bind that organization to these Terms.
          </p>

          <!-- Service Description -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">2. Service Description</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            vinReliability LLC provides engineering software for quality and reliability professionals:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>vinQuality:</strong> A cloud-based Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) quality management system for managing nonconformances, deviations, corrective actions, and supplier corrective actions.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>vinFMEA:</strong> A SaaS and desktop application for Failure Mode and Effects Analysis, including DFMEA, PFMEA, and FMEA-MSR with integrated control plans.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>vinReliability:</strong> A desktop software application for statistical analysis, Weibull modeling, reliability prediction, and related engineering calculations.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify, update, or discontinue features of our products at any time. We will provide reasonable notice for material changes that affect your use of the service.
          </p>

          <!-- Account Registration -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">3. Account Registration</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            To use our SaaS products, you must create an account and provide accurate, complete information. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account. You must notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            You may not share your account credentials with others or allow multiple individuals to use a single account unless your subscription plan explicitly permits it.
          </p>

          <!-- Subscription & Payments -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">4. Subscription and Payments</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            SaaS subscriptions (vinQuality and vinFMEA) are billed on a monthly or annual basis as selected at the time of purchase. Desktop software licenses (vinReliability) are billed annually. All fees are stated in US Dollars and are non-refundable except as required by applicable law.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Billing:</strong> Subscriptions renew automatically at the end of each billing period unless cancelled before the renewal date.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Price Changes:</strong> We may adjust pricing with at least 30 days written notice. Price changes take effect at the start of the next billing period.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Taxes:</strong> Prices do not include applicable taxes. You are responsible for any sales tax, VAT, or similar taxes imposed by your jurisdiction.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Intellectual Property -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            All intellectual property rights in our products, including software, documentation, designs, trademarks, and content, are owned by vinReliability LLC. Your subscription grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the software for your internal business purposes during the subscription term.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            You retain ownership of all data you enter into our products. We do not claim any intellectual property rights over your content. You grant us a limited license to host, store, and process your data solely for the purpose of providing the service.
          </p>

          <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, vinReliability LLC shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits, revenue, data, or business opportunities arising out of or related to your use of our products.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our total aggregate liability for any claims arising from these Terms or your use of the service shall not exceed the total amount paid by you to vinReliability LLC during the twelve (12) months preceding the claim.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our products are provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.
          </p>

          <!-- Termination -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">7. Termination</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            You may cancel your subscription at any time through your account settings or by contacting support. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period, and you will retain access to the service until that date.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We may suspend or terminate your account if you violate these Terms, fail to pay applicable fees, or engage in activity that harms the service or other users. In the event of termination for cause, no refund will be issued for the remaining subscription period.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Upon termination, your data will be retained for 90 days to allow for export. After 90 days, your data will be securely deleted from our systems.
          </p>

          <!-- Governing Law -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United States. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of our products shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the rules of the American Arbitration Association, unless both parties agree to resolve the dispute in a court of competent jurisdiction.
          </p>

          <!-- Changes to Terms -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify you of material changes by posting the updated Terms on our website and, where appropriate, by sending an email notification. Your continued use of the service after the effective date of the updated Terms constitutes your acceptance of the changes.
          </p>

          <!-- Contact -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">10. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
            <p class="text-base text-slate-700 font-semibold">vinReliability LLC</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Email: <a href="mailto:support@vinreliability.net" class="text-[#0D9488] hover:text-[#0F766E] transition-colors">support@vinreliability.net</a>
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Website: <a href="https://vinqms.com" class="text-[#0D9488] hover:text-[#0F766E] transition-colors">vinqms.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
